                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "L'ours rugir, et pleurer le bouleau des rivages,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Ses cheveux flamboyaient dans le brouillard amer.",
